data.description: Fabulous move in ready home in the best part of Bellevue. Just minutes to Percy Warner Park and the Harpeth River. If you golf you will love being so close to Harpeth Valley Golf Center. One mile to grocery,shopping and restaurants. Upstairs is all hardwood floors.Kitchen has granite counters. Stainless steel appliances. Refrigerator is one year old. Kitchen has loads of cabinets including two lazy susans and a pantry.  Primary bedroom upstairs has two closets. Downstairs is a very large den/ rec room /bedroom with a fireplace and a full size bathroom. This would make a perfect Primary suite and has an attached sun room with opening windows and screens. The garage is a full two car garage with plenty of extra storage space. Water heater is 1.5 years old. HVAC is 1 year old. Roof is less than a year old. Move in with no worries!!!!! Windows are double hung insulated windows which are easy to clean. Shed and Play area remain on this huge lot! FHA loan may be assumable at 3.5%
